To get started:

1) install node.js

e.g. ```brew install node```

2) install node libraries for project

```npm install```

3) install browserify globally

```npm install browserify -g```

4) generate bundle.js

```browserify src/main.js -o bundle.js```

5) (optional) use watchify to automatically regenerate bundle.js as you edit

```npm install watchify -g```
```watchify src/main.js -o bundle.js```